Stadion Funds
























Stadion Funds










Staying at the Dance Too Long
Bull market gains can become mediocre returns across full market cycles.
Learn more about it here.



Outcome Oriented for 12 Years
The Stadion Tactical Growth Fund has delivered strong, consistent performance through the short, medium and long term.
Learn more about it here.





12





Strategies with a defensive bias.
Stadion’s approach is simple but powerful: Over time, our goal is to capture most of the market's good times and miss most of its bad times. We believe that missing severe market drops is essential to investment success, because the less investors lose during downturns, the less they have to make up before their gains become true gains during a rebound. Making money is important, but protecting that money can be just as important.
We believe our active management strategies set us apart from many investment managers who employ buy-and-hold methodologies. We don't pretend to predict the market—that would be foolish. Rather, our proprietary processes are based on math and discipline. Our data-driven models recommend investment changes based on market conditions, and our money managers make changes to the Stadion portfolios and funds based solely on these indicators.





