Company Overview of Stadion Investment Trust - Stadion Tactical Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Stadion Investment Trust - Stadion Tactical Growth Fund is an open ended fund of fund launched and managed by Aviemore Asset Management, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It also makes its investments in funds. The fund primarily invest in exchange traded fund to create its portfolio. It invests in the growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization. The fund employs quantitative analysis with a focus on factors such as price movement, volatility, price to earnings ratios, growth rates, price to cash flow, and price to book ratios to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. The...
Stadion Investment Trust - Stadion Tactical Growth Fund is an open ended fund of fund launched and managed by Aviemore Asset Management, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It also makes its investments in funds. The fund primarily invest in exchange traded fund to create its portfolio. It invests in the growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization. The fund employs quantitative analysis with a focus on factors such as price movement, volatility, price to earnings ratios, growth rates, price to cash flow, and price to book ratios to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. The fund conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was formerly known as Stadion Investment Trust - Stadion Market Opportunity Fund. Stadion Investment Trust - Stadion Tactical Growth Fund was formed on May 3, 2004 and is domiciled in the United States.
